'''法式文胸'''或'''法式内衣'''（英文：Bralette）是一种没有钢圈的轻质[[文胸|文胸]]，主要为舒适而设计<ref name=Dyett/><ref>Emma Seymour, [https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/clothing/bra-reviews/g32406007/best-bralettes/ 17 Comfortable Bralettes of All Shapes and Sizes to Wear at Home], ''Good Housekeeping'', 2020-05-18<br />Bernadette Deron, [https://www.usmagazine.com/shop-with-us/news/mae-plunge-racerback-lace-bralette-comfy-bra-amazon-fashion/ No Underwire Here! You’ll Wish You Bought This Plunge Bralette Sooner], ''US Magazine'', 2020-06-18<br />Abigail Southan, [https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/fashion/style/g31927197/bralette/ Best bralettes to shop for women of all bust sizes], ''Cosmopolitan'', 2020-03-27<br />Tembe Denton-Hurst, [https://www.nylon.com/old-navy-bralette-review This $20 bralette actually supports my big boobs], ''Nylon''</ref>。
法式文胸有时也用作外套上衣<ref name=Dyett>Linda Dyett, [https://www.nytimes.com/2019/07/31/fashion/bralettes-bras-no-underwire.html?auth=login-google The Bralette Is Back. This Time Blouses Are Optional], ''The New York Times'', 2019-07-31</ref>，也设计为乳房发育中的女性的[[汗衫|汗衫]]<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/09/fashion/Bras-for-Grade-School-Girls-Bralettes.html The Playground Set Gets Its Own Bras]; URL accessed August 22, 2020.</ref>。

== 流行 ==
21世紀10年代到20年代初，法式文胸和软文胸开始流行，有[[鋼圈胸罩|钢圈]]和带衬垫的文胸逐渐被淘汰<ref>Georgina Safe, [https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2020/feb/07/cup-half-full-the-lingerie-brands-ditching-padding-and-underwire Cup half full: the lingerie brands ditching padding and underwire], ''The Guardian'', 2020-02-06</ref><ref name="Dyett" /> 。
包括[[维多利亚的秘密|维多利亚的秘密]]在内的部分品牌未能顺应这一趋势进行调整；因此，它们的销售额显着下降<ref>VerityJohnson, [https://www.stuff.co.nz/opinion/119318478/woke-millennials-didnt-kill-victorias-secret-pale-stale-males-did Woke millennials didn't kill Victoria's Secret, pale stale males did], ''Stuff'', 2020-02-07</ref>。2017 年，-{zh-cn:聚拢文胸;zh-tw:集中型胸罩;}-的销售额下降了45%，而[[马莎百货|马莎百货]]无鋼圈文胸的销售额则增长了40%<ref>Harriet Walker, [https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/push-up-bras-prove-a-bad-fit-for-women-in-era-of-metoo-fgfn627px Push-up bras prove a bad fit for women in era of #MeToo], ''The Times'', 2018-10-27</ref>。 一些人将法式文胸的日益流行归因于人们对“运动、健康和幸福”的逐渐关注，而不是为了“反对[[男性凝视|男性凝视]]”<ref>Kate Finnigan, [https://www.ft.com/content/69ef346e-6ccf-451b-bee2-03bdf4b77a02 Soft focus: the new lingerie evolution], ''Financial Times'', 2020-07-08</ref> 
，而另一些人则认为与[[#MeToo|#MeToo运动]]有-{zh-cn:联系;zh-tw:關聯;}-<ref name=Dyett/>。

由于人们更注重[[远程工作|-{zh-cn:远程;zh-tw:遠距;}-辦公]]时的舒适度，在[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|-{zh-cn:新型冠状病毒大流行;zh-tw:嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎疫情;}-]]期间，法式文胸也变得流行起来。
